messages.message: I was thinking of getting up there early too, so we wont have to set up in the dark. I don't know if it will be needed, but I packed my gigantic 8-10 person tent as well as my 2 person tent. I have a couple extra sleeping bags and chairs, so if anyone needs one just let me know.

Brian
We will definitely need some extra tent space, sounds awesome, we look forward to seeing you!
Also, would you still be able to join us if we don't end up at lake ashurst?

Yeah, I can camp wherever just let me know what you guys decide.
I think my parents were gonna camp somewhere near ashurst  so it would have been convenient because they are staying until Sunday and I was gonna switch camps after you guys leave. Its fine with me either way though.

Brian
Hi
Hey, haven't seen you in a while.

Brian
hi
I am living in Scottsdale now, we should meet up for a drink or something.
I don't have many friends here, and they flake out a lot.
Steve and Elyse are in Glendale which is stupid far.
how have you been?

yeah we should
yeah I dont have a lot of friends here either
I'm pretty good, but am lookin for a new job
what about you?
haha I finally got a new phone...so now I can compete in your wierd little phone competition.

Brian
haha, there is no more phone competition
I already won
game over 
I got a job working for a medical device statup
I make pretty good money.

Brian
I make pretty good money.
lol whatever

Brian
I am lucky, I get to do what I enjoy, which is write code and manage the network

thats awesome
I volunteer for the Mesa crime lab...but it is incredibly hard to get a job there

Brian
why's that?

hiring freeze
or someone needs to die lol

Brian
oh..
well, you could off someone, but then your department would probably figure it out
haha thats why I have to volunteer a little longer until I figure out how to cover my tracks

Brian
 good plan
do you watch Dexter?
I'm not sure if I'm up to date on it..but yeah I love that show

Brian
haha me too.

Brian
so how come you're home on a Saturday night?

I have to babysit
why are you home on a sat night?

Brian
sorry, my internet went out.  I am writing code.  Starting a new website called tune gazelle.

Brian
Thank you for connecting!
